list.name: Changes
list.comment: The FileSystemCrawlerFactory tries for 'txt' files the 'csv' crawler first and if it gains any tables (meaning that it went through all the 'filters' of detect_delimiters() and creating the dataframe) the csv Crawler is assigned to the txt file - the container has 'csv' Crawler eventhough it's a 'txt' file
